I know a little great place.

356
00:23:45,157 --> 00:23:46,852
Do you use The Method?

357
00:23:50,228 --> 00:23:51,923
Do we have to do this now?

358
00:23:51,997 --> 00:23:53,589
Yeah. That's the thing.

359
00:23:53,665 --> 00:23:56,225
I have to do it,
even if I don't want to.

360
00:23:56,301 --> 00:23:58,929
It's the only way
to be honest and real.

361
00:24:00,005 --> 00:24:01,632
