372
00:24:49,187 --> 00:24:51,747
I have to stay focused.
Complete honesty.

373
00:24:51,823 --> 00:24:53,051
Do you love me?

374
00:24:54,392 --> 00:24:56,053
You know how I feel about you.

375
00:24:56,127 --> 00:24:59,426
