in front of my camera?

376
00:24:59,498 --> 00:25:02,023
Why can't you just say it?

377
00:25:03,568 --> 00:25:07,504
I sew your ripped pants.
I trip over your camera.

378
00:25:09,107 --> 00:25:10,802
