379
00:25:10,876 --> 00:25:14,334
I just don't
want to run out of film.

380
00:25:15,714 --> 00:25:17,807
What are you looking for?

381
00:25:17,883 --> 00:25:20,408
What do you mean?

382
00:25:20,485 --> 00:25:22,715
What is your biggest wish?

383
00:25:27,993 --> 00:25:30,894
That cats could talk.

384
00:25:30,962 --> 00:25:33,226
Something that girl said,
isn't it?

385
00:25:33,298 --> 00:25:35,493
What are you talking about?
You're being silly.

386
00:25:35,567 --> 00:25:38,365
I thought you had to be
totally honest in this film.

387
00:25:38,436 --> 00:25:40,233
I am.

388
00:25:41,273 --> 00:25:42,797
You're being ridiculous.

389
00:25:42,874 --> 00:25:44,569
Who said that? That actress?

390
00:25:44,643 --> 00:25:46,372
You want to sleep with her!

391
00:25:46,444 --> 00:25:49,811
-Now, that's ridiculous.
-What is your problem?

392
00:25:49,881 --> 00:25:52,406
I can't believe you!
I just don't understand!

393
00:25:52,484 --> 00:25:54,247
We need to talk.

394
00:26:01,126 --> 00:26:04,425
Hey, Paul.
Ready to go to the party?

395
00:26:10,368 --> 00:26:11,835
Let me drive.

396
00:26:14,806 --> 00:26:17,104
Did you pass
your driving test finally?

397
00:26:26,785 --> 00:26:28,753
Maybe you can drive
on the way home.

398
00:27:43,895 --> 00:27:45,692
I got a call from the hospital.

399
00:27:45,764 --> 00:27:48,096
Felix was in a car accident.

400
00:27:48,166 --> 00:27:50,498
Smashed up his Alfa.

401
00:27:50,568 --> 00:27:53,560
The doctor said he was OK.

402
00:27:53,638 --> 00:27:55,970
Just broke his leg.

403
00:27:56,041 --> 00:27:57,906
He's getting out of
the Dragonfly picture...

404
00:27:57,976 --> 00:27:59,273
